{"tid":42036,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英小男孩遭欺凌  大漢組車隊護送","createTime":"2016-12-16T10:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T22:24:17.000Z","uid":36494,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"624b9a4d617131bc0ea4259a346461483be1e22b","tid":42036,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:42:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161216/bknint-20161216122612034-1216_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161216%2Fbknint-20161216122612034-1216_17011_001.html&d=pV8d1d37%2BPc5ZieEQmfScQv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=16f58b1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161216/bknint-20161216122612034-1216_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a54a8c26f9c8eb60760d935937baade3df980b0b","tid":42036,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45027ee1ab0bf3d31c7543c1880aa33dfbab0e7","tid":42036,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:54:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=pV8d1d37%2BPc5ZieEQmfScQv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=59795098\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a> 東網專訊】英國2名男孩被街頭少年欺凌長達幾個月，由一批雄赳赳大漢組成的反對欺凌車隊協會得知後，組成了一個40人的車隊前來聲援，令他們終於可以重拾信心，不怕出門。<br />\n<br />\n斯蒂文森來自英國的拉克霍爾，今年7歲。他最好的朋友特倫斯今年8歲，2人近數個月來不斷被一群街頭少年欺負，少年嘲笑2個小男孩的身高和穿著，甚至還用電插頭等物打他們。特倫斯母親表示，2個男孩很怕離家上學，學校卻一點忙都幫不上。她試圖找少年的父母交涉，卻無功而還。<br />\n<br />\n特倫斯的叔叔安德魯於是請反對欺凌車隊協會前來幫忙，護送2個小男孩出門。斯蒂文森和特倫斯沒想到會有40人來幫他們，車隊的隊員們還和2個小男孩分享自己的故事，說他們小時候也曾經被欺負過。<br />\n<br />\n反對欺凌車隊協會最初在美國成立，旨在支持反霸凌運動。英國人庫珀今年6月在該國成立分部，他的2個小孩曾被欺凌長達一年，9歲的兒子甚至曾被打到骨折。"},{"pid":"be9b18bd9e1e19258bb6125a24c8343e25a54f05","tid":42036,"uid":28644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:57:22.000Z","msg":"Thug life<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1502174bc1f86f63f1d72ad1a8120edc4b48e72a","tid":42036,"uid":57646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T10:58:03.000Z","msg":"街童正垃圾"},{"pid":"7278114a8c93a7284261647ffe33f693e7f20c28","tid":42036,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p2fAV0q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp2fAV0q.jpg&h=f29cf7ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/190111_5c1442bded9f465b9f7248bfc3a6c9cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F190111_5c1442bded9f465b9f7248bfc3a6c9cf.jpg&h=287c8fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/16/190113_66f181f7281ffb0cd94d3eb2249eea07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F16%2F190113_66f181f7281ffb0cd94d3eb2249eea07.jpg&h=485b2629&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d331e1ad99d17b23743cdb5a739a9f56a6f61ff","tid":42036,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:27:07.000Z","msg":"D仆街MK仔捉去打靶就岩喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596533f06492f0e63caae48fe60b18c9c1b1a629","tid":42036,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:29:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4063540d6b154cfb0d5155d30772ffefafe8ff","tid":42036,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T11:30:23.000Z","msg":"學英文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-4017246/Dozens-b